Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I met Gin Minowa for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like she was a difficult\Nperson to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I got overwhelmed by her loud voice\Nand her aggressiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I got to know her,\Nshe was actually a really nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who would have thought\Nshe would blank and blank?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Half a month after finishing our first job
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,as heroes protecting humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the second enemy appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That spinning thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be weak against an attack from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do. This is unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. I have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Namuhachiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bodhisattva.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Minowa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a limit to bulldozing your way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:02:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many lives\Nyou all have, it won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a good job by
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,keeping the damage to the\Nreal world to a minimum, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's thanks to Minowa-san and Nogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weak point is not having\Nenough practice working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,First let's decide on a leader\Nwithin the three of you to take charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader? That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you to be the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the leader type.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So as long as it's not me, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nogi family have great power over the amnesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's from a lineage that should be\Nchosen as the leader in a situation like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I also agree that you should be the leader, Nogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm the one who will\Nactually have to unite them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, I'm going to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's decided, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the oracle,\Nwe have some time before the next attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do a training camp\Nto strengthen your coordination skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you and start running\NTo a place where no one can catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to fulfill it\NThe promise from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki Yuna is a Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A bud of happiness in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It had a silver glow\NI'll show it to you when it blossoms
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In the album that I looked back on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like that back then, and it still is now\NWe're laughing together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:04:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The season which gets colored from the south
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, say "I'm back"\NI'll definitely come to welcome you straight away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you and start running\NTo a place where no one can catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to fulfill it\NThe promise from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you patiently for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back\NPlease, don't ever leave me again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 2\NFRIENDS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,RESERVED FOR SHINJYU HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Minowa-san is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry that I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ten minutes late, even though\Nyou were so eager. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm the one who's at fault, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm sorry, Sumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me give you an advice on this occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your lifestyle is too sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have an awareness\Nthat you were chosen as a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have to be the reliable one after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can protect this beautiful country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,SANSHU\NSUN BEACH
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Since your role has officially started,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the amnesty will fully back you all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about your family\Nor school, and do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready? The rules for this training are simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You must safely get Minowa-san to that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget each other's roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Defend me properly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not allowed to move from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we not jump from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an easy win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-Out.\N-I'm sorry, Minowa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What you call me is too formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just call me Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And call me Sonocchi.\NOkay, try calling us that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to do this till you can reach the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You must do everything together\Nduring this training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to make one plus one plus one\Na ten instead of a three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasshi, are those all your things? It's not a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san, you're buying souvenirs way too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your luggage, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know where to begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make udon with that stone mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Out. Start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore Shinjyu-sama made the wall\Nso it will protect the humans from the viruses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we wouldn't have\Nto study during the training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However, something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi-san, can you answer what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am. Vertex was born\Nand started attacking our home, Shikoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She was actually listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Booyah, this should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating balanced meals, getting disciplined intensely,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and getting proper sleep every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like a training camp\Nfor a sports club, instead of heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't there be an event where\Nwe can learn a super killer move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Sumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a choice. We're doing this\Nto strengthen our coordination skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I gained more muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right to get stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's a difficult menu\Nfor pre-adolescent girls to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san, does your wound\Nfrom being caught in the tornado hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. How about you, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This stings more than anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, holding that thing will definitely do that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi Washio, show us your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to admire the biggest breasts in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if this is a fruit shop.\NGive me those peaches, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I only said the truth.\NIf anything, you're expecting too much
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,by being self-conscious about having big breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish Sancho could be part of this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Minowa-san and Washio-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be too loud in the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, the body of an adult is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really tell when they're wearing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It's kind of like Battleship Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a battleship our country\Nproudly had in the former century.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about it in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys think you can sleep that easily\Non the last day of training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought my own pillow, so I can sleep easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What was its name? Tacos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sancho. There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Sonoko-san, what's with your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a chicken. I like charbroiled chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, it is tasty.\N-At any rate, we shouldn't stay up this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're at your own pace, aren't you, Sumi?\N-If you don't listen to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll come and get you in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll come and get us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying horrifying things,\Nand let's share who we have a crush on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As in someone we like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Minowa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to choose, it would be my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Family members don't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anyone either, so it's even.\NWhat about you, Nogi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, is it time for girl talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Is it someone from our class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. It's Wasshi and Mino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we okay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine. We have sacred roles to fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all work hard tomorrow too.\NTraining doesn't end until we are home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Fine.\N-Lights off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a planetarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it with me because it's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I had some business to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Some business?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,SET MEAL WITH GRILLED MEAT\NSOLIDITY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Minowa-san is late way too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But she never says why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she has her reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A cat? Why? It's so suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki Yuna is a Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost at Minowa-san's house. Nogi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an ant. Hey, hey, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go wandering off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,MINOWA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be Minowa-san's house.\NLet's see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are we going to ding dong ditch?\N-You shouldn't do such a terrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's use this. I brought this thinking\Nthat it might come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're like a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my little brother, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The only time you can cry is\Nwhen you realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't get back your New Year's money\Nyou entrusted to your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's getting cranky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably don't want milk,\Nor your diaper changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you stopped crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What a good boy, little bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a spoiled little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you my underling and\Npush you around once you're grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you get used to our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, what about the errands?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Mino-san is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's babysitting and helping with housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know she had such young brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's having\Na hard time looking after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Wasshi, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he asked her for directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san is so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's putting the bicycle back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Mino-san has a tendency\Nto get involved in incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this is because she's a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lost child this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mediating a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of being caught up in it,\Nit's more like she can't leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't watch this anymore. Minowa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-We'll help you.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you guys have been watching me\Nfrom the front of my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel kind of embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't feel embarrassed. It's admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is why you're always late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do that, it's as if I'm blaming it on other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, it is my fault for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you always had that tendency?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm unlucky most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never won anything in a bingo either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Our Sunday is ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a visual kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll survey the situation first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because of that enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This time for sure. This time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, Sumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Minowa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's defeat it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's use what we learned at training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get close to the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Roger that.\N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taken command of the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to launch something at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Willpower!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mino-san!\N-I can hold it off for at least a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get the enemy up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But Minowa-san will be in danger if we do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? There's going to be\Ndamage to the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And Minowa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us will strike the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wasshi, get up there.\N-What? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mino-san!\N-Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shatter it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready for a triple payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the change!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceremony of chinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle was hard on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to attack it\Nbecause you were taking its attack like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You did great too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you said you could\Nhold it off for one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I knew it would work out okay\Nif we had that much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been dangerous\Nif we had dragged it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our teacher saw through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:21:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi-san's inspiration at a critical moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I just kept on debating what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I assumed Nogi-san got chosen\Nbecause of her family lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a huge idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking I had to be the reliable one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was just dragging them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in the middle of eating udon, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-What's wrong, Sumi? Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll go along\Nwith you guys from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:21:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like we're finally friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a story of three heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A fairy tale of three girls who were chosen by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always an innocent girl who gets chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And in many cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the end result is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.91,0:24:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,ON THE NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is this feeling?\N-I'm so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.83,0:24:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's enjoy.\N-What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.79,0:24:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-I got a love letter too?\N-It's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hooray!\N-Let the fun time off begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE\NEVERYDAY LIFE
